item.title: CVE-2020-7816|2024-08-04T09:41:01.907Z -- human%20talk -- daview%20indy%2C%20dava%2B%2C%20daoffice
item.description: A vulnerability in the JPEG image parsing module in DaView Indy, DaVa+, DaOffice softwares could allow an unauthenticated, remote attacker to cause an arbitrary code execution on an affected device.nThe vulnerability is due to a stack overflow read. An attacker could exploit this vulnerability by sending a crafted PDF file to an affected device.
